    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
