    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute beauty! I have babied this car since day one, and it is honestly in breathtaking, like-new condition. Not a single scratch, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019m so sad to let it go, but I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will love it as much as I do. It's a total gem\u2014come grab it before someone else does!",
      "price": 43500.0,
