    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains structurally flawless with proactive subframe reinforcement and a recently overhauled VANOS system. Every mechanical component, from the M Variable Differential Lock to the factory-spec bushings, retains its tactile precision. This is a collector-tier specimen with a comprehensive service dossier, showcasing a level of preservation rarely seen in the modern market.",
